  "title": "Brand Ambassador – Sales & Marketing Role 🌟📢",
  "description": "<p>📍 Singapore | Full-Time </p><p>As a Brand Ambassador, you’ll represent our clients professionally at event sites, communicate brand value, and create meaningful customer experiences.</p><p>You’ll work closely with a team while developing communication, presentation, and leadership skills.</p><p><strong>Ideal for:</strong> Confident communicators who enjoy representing brands and connecting with people.<br /><br /><strong>Requirements / What We’re Looking For</strong></p><p><ul><li>🗣 Confident communicator</li><li>😊 Professional and positive image</li><li>🤝 Enjoys engaging with people</li></ul></p><p><strong>Responsibilities / What You’ll Be Doing</strong></p><p><ul><li>🌟 Represent client brands at events/roadshows</li><li>🗣 Communicate product value effectively</li><li>🤝 Create positive customer experiences</li></ul></p><p><strong>Benefits / What You’ll Gain</strong></p><p><ul><li>🌟 Brand representation experience</li><li>📈 Communication and presentation skills</li><li>🚀 Leadership and career growth opportunities</li><li>🌍 Travelling Opportunities</li></ul></p>",
